{"title":"同时使用ORDER BY 和GROUP BY","date":"2019-01-16T01:09:18.000Z","link":"post/295","categories":["DataBase"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:19:38.363Z","content":"<p><code>注：GROUP BY 子句使用时必须放在 WHERE 子句中的条件之后，必须放在 ORDER BY 子句之前。</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"附：SQL执行顺序进行解读：\">附：SQL执行顺序进行解读：<a href=\"post/295#附：SQL执行顺序进行解读：\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">　　(1)from </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(2) join</span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(3) on </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(4) where </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(5)group by</span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(6) avg,sum.... （组函数）</span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(7)having </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(8) select </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(9) distinct </span><br><span class=\"line\">　　(10) order by</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"linux的rz安装","link":"post/296"},"next":{"title":"Java StringBuffer insert()方法","link":"post/294"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/295/"}